#Using a SQL injection UNION attack to retrieve interesting data
Pehle pata karo original query kitne columns return karti hai.
Dekho kaunse columns string data le sakte hain.
Agar table users hai aur columns username & password, injection yeh hoga:
' UNION SELECT username, password FROM users--
Ye WHERE clause me quoted string ke andar use hota hai.
Agar table/column names nahi pata, pehle database structure check karna padega.

